com.example.volkerpetersen.sailingrace

Class fifoQueueDouble

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.volkerpetersen.sailingrace.fifoQueueDouble

  • public class fifoQueueDouble
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to initialize and manage a FIFO queue for double variables. Each new instance for another variable gets initialized with a size (# of elements in the FIFO queue)
